# Serial Command Interface

## Objective

Develop a Serial Command Interface to control the built-in LED of the Arduino UNO using commands entered through the Serial Monitor.

## Components

- Arduino UNO

## Supported Commands

- LED_ON
- LED_OFF
- BLINK X (1–9)
- STATUS
- RESET

## Features

- Controls the built-in LED.
- Blinks the LED a specified number of times.
- Displays LED status and blink counter.
- Handles invalid commands gracefully.

